+ Install **zsh** `zypper in zsh` and **git** `zypper in git`.
+ Then install **oh-my-zsh** `wget --no-check-certificate http://install.ohmyz.sh -O - | sh`.
+ Then define **zsh** as your default shell: `chsh -s /bin/zsh`.
